com.davidsoergel.conja

Class IteratorAsThreadSafeNextOnlyIterator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.davidsoergel.conja.IteratorAsThreadSafeNextOnlyIterator<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ThreadSafeNextOnlyIterator<T>

    public class IteratorAsThreadSafeNextOnlyIterator<T>
extends Object
implements ThreadSafeNextOnlyIterator<T>
    Ensures that every next() call is synchronized. It is important for the underlying iterator not to be modified (some will throw ConcurrentModificationException in this case, but that's not guaranteed).
